data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. MULTIPLE OFFERS RECEIVED.  HIGHEST AND BEST DUE BY 5PM FEBRUARY 1ST.  *** SPACIOUS 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom, 1 Car Garage home located on huge CORNER LOT in Port Charlotte.  ***  NEW ROOF & AC with PUBLIC WATER AND PUBLIC SEWER!!  Just needs a little cosmetic TLC, including new living room flooring and screens on lanai.  Should be good for even an FHA mortgage. *** NO HOA FEES! *** Highly desired split bedroom floor plan! *** The spacious master bedroom has a private bathroom and sliding door to the lanai. A screened-in lanai is the perfect spot for enjoying the BEAUTIFUL Florida weather.  A large open yard offers a nice sized storage shed and provides many opportunities. *** New flood insurance policy is transferable, currently $2501/year ***   Excellent location in a quiet neighborhood yet close to everything!!! Very convenient to Port Charlotte & Downtown Punta Gorda, Shopping & Dining, Gulf beaches, BEST GOLFING, BOATING AND FISHING IN SOUTHWEST FLORIDA, medical, schools, Charlotte County Sports Stadium – home of Tampa Bay Rays Spring Training, and so much more!!! Enjoy fishing or kayaking practically in your back yard or go boating out to the Harbor and the Gulf via nearby boat ramps for a great day of fun in the sun!!! *** All measurements and details provided should be verified by buyers.
